2024 Client Feedback Survey Data

Introduction

The following report presents data visualizations from the 2024 Client Feedback Survey, which gathered feedback from clients receiving services across CoC projects. These visualizations summarize responses across all projects rather than by individual project. This approach was taken because some projects had very few responses which would not provide meaningful insights at the project level.

The report is structured into five sections, each focusing on a specific survey question. Responses are broken down by age group, chronic status, gender, and race/ethnicity to highlight trends and disparities among different populations. Our goal is to provide a clearer understanding of client experiences and identify areas for improvement in service delivery.

Note on Race/Ethnicity Data: Some survey respondents did not select a race/ethnicity category, resulting in responses categorized as Data Not Collected. Since this category does not provide meaningful insights into racial disparities, we have excluded these responses from the Race/Ethnicity visualizations. However, their responses are still included in the other demographic breakdowns.
